{"tid":2192521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中芯國際】瑞信：中芯若受美國制裁 對中國5G進程影響有限","createTime":"2020-09-07T07:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T12:56:01.000Z","uid":53062,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"be66aaf982ce8544b7b018833ef79304788193a4","tid":2192521,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:36:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2746055/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E8%8A%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E3%80%91%E7%91%9E%E4%BF%A1%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E8%8A%AF%E8%8B%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%20%20%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B5G%E9%80%B2%E7%A8%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2746055%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258A%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2591%259E%25E4%25BF%25A1%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258A%25AF%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%2520%2520%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B5G%25E9%2580%25B2%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2599%2590&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=b7b553e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2746055/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E8%8A%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E3%80%91%E7%91%9E%E4%BF%A1%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E8%8A%AF%E8%8B%A5%E5%8F%97%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%20%20%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B5G%E9%80%B2%E7%A8%8B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90</a><br />\n<br />\n中芯國際 （00981） 或被列入美國貿易黑名單，股價今日重挫2成。瑞信亞洲科技研究部門主管Manish Nigam認為，過去屢有傳言美國會將某家中國公司列入黑名單，目前尚無法證實中芯會否遭美國制裁。但即使中芯遭制裁，不認為中國的5G手機、系統建設將停滯，依然有其他渠道可獲取5G相關晶片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑞信亞洲半導體分析師Randy Abrams指，中芯國際在晶圓代工廠的市佔較低，且公司90%以上收入來自40nm或以上的成熟工藝，先進工藝收入佔比不足10%，將有其他廠商可彌補中芯空缺，同時台積電TSMC（台：2330）、聯電（台：2303）均有發展中國業務，未虞中國5G進程受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2b0cb5102d21a68cfaa278abd6789fe58350ef","tid":2192521,"uid":124616,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"40nm 勁撚到"},{"pid":"f6d28891dcfea5496a7376e0cf4cbde6f1d686d5","tid":2192521,"uid":83102,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bc2b0cb5102d21a68cfaa278abd6789fe58350ef","tid":2192521,"uid":124616,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"40nm 勁撚到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"台積電都淨係得3nm<br />\n中芯做到40nm量產<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1d554f445f1d84d33179ea6029a4eada5f1ffa","tid":2192521,"uid":180401,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f6d28891dcfea5496a7376e0cf4cbde6f1d686d5","tid":2192521,"uid":83102,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"bc2b0cb5102d21a68cfaa278abd6789fe58350ef","tid":2192521,"uid":124616,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"40nm 勁撚到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"台積電都淨係得3nm<br />\n中芯做到40nm量產<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:05:49.000Z","msg":"禁大粒一定好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efd2a1252fcefc6d1234f513ae1461a94c74bdc","tid":2192521,"uid":306621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"制裁對5G 無影響<br />\n唔代表對中芯無影響<br />\n樓主要搞清楚  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454d6ed9e161ee05956d3d6f1aedea7cbfa1813f","tid":2192521,"uid":342828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"終國又成最大贏家！老美出親D招都無嚟殺傷力